{"id": 2461, "genre": 1000, "title": "为了维持动力，你都试过哪些打鸡血的方式？", "description": "自制力薄弱星人的挣扎，请在留言区自曝补充。（题图来自：istock © jossdim）", "record_count": 6958, "comment_count": 38, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201807101824247yiIocZxsNmefdYR.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-07-12T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4496, "title": "为了维持动力，你都试过哪些打鸡血的方式？", "content": "为了维持动力，你都试过哪些打鸡血的方式？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 291928, "content": "把事情都堆到deadline最后一刻，激发最大潜能", "image": "img/option/option/20180710182541UcOtWhuTEKHwl8e6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 291930, "content": "对自己放狠话，屏保是“还吃！滚去背书！再买剁手！”", "image": "img/option/option/20180710183051UfPuSn7158WYVALT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 291931, "content": "减肥箴言贴桌角，“今天少吃一口肉，明天维密我走秀”", "image": "img/option/option/20180710183208a4jpyOHRNfTr5sie.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 291932, "content": "熟背各种热血台词，“教练，我想打篮球”", "image": "img/option/option/20180710183536Bba9H1oSmkAjdlZI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 291934, "content": "定期拍（没啥差别的）减肥前后对比照", "image": "img/option/option/20180710183731grPbO6EStwsy3cuv.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 291936, "content": "小一号的好看衣服，“瘦下来就能穿上了”", "image": "img/option/option/20180710184337BtFaiPfXsHxyoYIv.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 291937, "content": "松懈的时候，看一眼每月的还款账单", "image": "img/option/option/20180710184420xquaFgOnAYNsyeJ9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 291939, "content": "把自拍做成表情包，配文“我很饿但是我有出息我不说”", "image": "img/option/option/20180710184655Ea1Mr75gHQIY9GU0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 291940, "content": "把网络id换成“不瘦10斤不改名”", "image": "img/option/option/20180710185011pq6f8AcCFTyLZVn9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 291941, "content": "买kindle/跑步机/吉他…“只要跟它们呆满一万小时...”", "image